data.description: Beautiful country home on 2 acres of land in the heart of middle Georgia. All brick home with large wired 30 x 30 workshop and many updates throughout home. Every bedroom has its own en suite bathroom. No carpet - gorgeous engineered hardwood and tile. Quartz countertops, high ceilings and stunning stone fireplace. Back covered porch perfectly overlooks backyard and patio - featuring brick firepit. This home is made for entertaining! Seller is related to listing agent.
